Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,正在高速接近，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Coming up on it fast, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.47,0:00:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你能确定传感器的读数吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you certain of your sensor readings?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,确定为某种飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Definitely a space vessel of some type.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来源？ - 未知\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Origin? - Unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.97,0:00:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能是地球飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It could hardly be an Earth ship. There have been no flights
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这一地区已多年没有航线 - 拦截到信号，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- into this sector for years. - I'm picking up a signal, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.98,0:00:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，是老式摩尔斯码信号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, that's the old Morse code call signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.48,0:00:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢，上尉 - C-Q，C-Q\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Thank you, lieutenant. - C-Q. C-Q.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们听到了，上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're reading it, lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.28,0:00:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得你说这不可能是地球飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought you said it couldn't possibly be an Earth vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.57,0:00:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不明白你为什么总喜欢看我出错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fail to understand why it always gives you pleasure to see me proven wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.16,0:00:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,地球人情感上的弱点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}An emotional Earth weakness of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:01:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是和DY-500型相似的老式地球飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}An old Earth vessel similar to the DY-500 class.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,比那更老，是DY-100型\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Much older. DY-100 class, to be exact.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.27,0:01:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.06,0:01:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,最后建造的这种飞船也远在20世纪90年代\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...the last such vessel was built centuries ago, back in the 1990s.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.69,0:01:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那飞船是被遗弃了，自动发射的信号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then it's a derelict, its signal left on automatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.15,0:01:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,或这艘老式地球飞船被外星人控制了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or an old Earth ship being used by aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.32,0:01:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 武装状态 - 导流护盾开到最大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Weapons status. - Deflector shields on maximum.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.87,0:01:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 相位炮手就位，长官 - 汇报生物扫描结果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Phasers manned, sir. - Bio-scanners report.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.49,0:01:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,生命扫描仪获得心跳信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Life science bio-scanners are picking up heartbeats from over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.04,0:01:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但不可能是人类，心跳太微弱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can't be human, though. They're too faint and average,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,平均每分钟四次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}only four beats per minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.00,0:01:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,传感器显示某种设备在这艘飞船上运作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sensor reading, captain. Some sort of equipment functioning on that vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,所有甲板，全面戒备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All decks, go to full alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙，最后的边疆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Space, the final frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.16,0:02:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这是星舰进取号的航程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These are the voyages of the starship Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,它的五年任务，是去探索未知的新世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Its five-year mission: to explore strange new worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,找寻新的生命与新的文明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to seek out new life and new civilizations,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.88,0:02:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,勇踏前人未至之境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to boldly go where no man has gone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,【星际迷航：原初】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}TLF荣誉出品\N本字幕仅供学习交流，严禁用于商业途径{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}-=TLF字幕组=-\N翻译：锁锁美同学\N校对：喜马拉雅 Micezhang{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,第一季第二十二集\N太空种子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历3141.9\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 3141.9.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,自拦截到陌生船只，已经过了一个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A full hour has elapsed since interception of the strange vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的出现仍完全被无视\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our presence alongside is still being completely ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然传感器显示船上仍然有设备运作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Although our sensors continue to show signs of equipment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,和生命迹象，但对我们已不构成威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and life aboard, there's been no indication of danger to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,武装部，保持战斗状态\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Weapons Department, maintain battle stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,其他部门，提高警觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All other decks, stand by alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所有部门都收到命令，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All decks acknowledging, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,还在收到心跳信号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Continuing to pick up some form of heart action over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,很微弱，很慢，依我推测\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very faint, very slow. Seems to be coming from about 60 or 70 bodies,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 似乎来自六七十个个体 - 是外星人吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- as near as I can make out. - Alien bodies, Bones?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是，没有呼吸或其他类似迹象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Could be. There's no sign of breathing or any other form of respiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,船体表面布满了流星坑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hull surface is pitted with meteor scars.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.21,0:03:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但扫描仪显示出“星舰-植物湾”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}However, scanners make out a name, SS Botany Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.17,0:03:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,可以查看注册表\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then you can check the registry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,注册表上没有这种型号的船只\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No such vessel listed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那一时期的记录只剩下片段了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Records of that period are fragmentary, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,90年代中期正好是你们最后一次「世界大战」\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The mid-1990s was the era of your last so-called "World War."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,优生之战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Eugenics Wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你们想通过优生优选来进化人种\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course. Your attempt to improve the race through selective breeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,打断一下，这不是我们的想法，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, wait a minute, not our attempt, Mr. Spock,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是一群雄心勃勃的科学家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a group of ambitious scientists.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你了解的类型\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sure you know the type:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,信仰理性，毫无感情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Devoted to logic, completely unemotional--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 医生，请你… - 好了，先生们，别闹了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Doctor, I would be pleased-- - All right, gentlemen, as you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,牵引光束，锁定该飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Rig for tractor beam, helm. Lock onto that vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 发射牵引光束，长官 - 接管舰桥，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Rigging for tractor beam, sir. - Bridge is yours, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.67,0:04:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,要加入登陆小队吗，医生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Care to join the landing party, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你真想让我选…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, if you're actually giving me a choice--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我才没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要一个熟悉20世纪地球的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, I'll need somebody familiar with the late 20th-century Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,该是历史学家大显身手的时候了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Here's a chance for that historian to do something for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,她叫什么？卖歌文？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's her name? McGivers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,麦戈文上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant McGivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,请注意，以下人员请去传送室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Attention. The following personnel report to Transporter Room:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,轮机长史考特，麦戈文上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Engineering Officer Scott, Lieutenant McGivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Acknowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.91,0:05:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,麦戈文收到，马上到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}McGivers, on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这艘船就像在等我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It looks like that ship is expecting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,热量读数在上升，空气中含有氧气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We read heat coming on, complete oxygen atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,有趣，准备好没，老骨头？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very interesting. You ready, Bones?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.76,0:05:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我被分配在船上行医\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. Signed aboard this ship to practise medicine,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是让我的分子被传来传去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}not to have my atoms scattered back and forth across space by this gadget.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你真守旧，麦考伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're an old-fashioned boy, McCoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,历史学家在哪儿？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where's that historian?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好，过来吧，麦… - 麦戈文，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Well, come on, Lieutenant... - McGivers, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,启动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Energize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Scotty?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.10,0:06:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,典型的地球式船舱，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Definitely Earth-type mechanisms, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,二十世纪的飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Twentieth-century vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,老式核能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Old-type atomic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,庞大、笨重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bulky, solid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我想这就是所谓的“晶体管单元”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think they used to call them "transistor units."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我很想拆开研究\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd love to tear this baby apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉，这是睡眠舱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, it's a sleeper ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,假死状态？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Suspended animation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾见过这样的老照片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've seen old photographs of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,直到大约2018年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Necessary because of the time involved
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,太空旅行都要进入这种假死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in space travel until about the year 2018.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,从一个星球到另一个星球会花费数年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It took years just to travel from one planet to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.63,0:06:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,经过几个世纪的旅行…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is it possible they're still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,…他们可能还活着？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...after centuries of travel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,理论上可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Theoretically possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我从没听过这种例子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've never heard of it being tested for this long a period.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他们真俊俏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What a handsome group of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，有新的数据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim, I have a new reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这些灯肯定触发了什么装置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lights must have triggered some mechanism.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.69,0:06:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，看这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Scotty?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我发生了什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Beats me what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,0:07:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们触发了某些装置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've triggered something, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,心跳加速，现在每分钟八次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Heartbeat's increasing, now passing eight beats per minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,发现开始呼吸的迹象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And there are some signs of respiration beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人可能最先醒来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This one was probably programmed to be triggered first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.51,0:07:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他是首领吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Could he be the leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.72,0:07:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,首领，上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The leader. Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.06,0:07:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，长官，首领会第一个复苏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, sir. The leader was often set to revive first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这样他就可以判断\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This would allow him to decide
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.94,0:07:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,当下环境是否适合其他人复苏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}whether the conditions warranted revival of the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.69,0:07:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,现在心跳接近每分钟四十次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Heartbeat now approaching 40 per minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,呼吸节奏稳步上升\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The respiration pattern is firming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.12,0:07:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为是来自印度北部地区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}From the northern India area, I'd guess,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是锡克人，他们是迷人的战士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}probably a Sikh. They're the most fantastic warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 心跳现在达到五十二，还在持续上升 - 其他人呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Heartbeat now 52 and increasing. - The others?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.92,0:07:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人没有变化，他们来自各个地区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's no change. And they're all mixed types:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:07:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,西方，欧洲中部，拉丁还有东方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Western, mid-European, Latin, Oriental.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,来自二十世纪的人类即将苏醒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A man from the 20th century coming alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不一定，心跳速率下降\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe. Heartbeat dropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,电路短路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Circuit shorting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.31,0:08:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是灰尘引起的，心率三十，在快速下降\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Probably some dust. Heartbeat now 30, dropping fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,心房颤动，他快死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's a heart flutter. He's dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 做点什么，舰长 - 可以吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Do something, captain. - Can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,花上一小时才能知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take an hour to figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,让他从里面出来会怎么样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What happens if we get him out of there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不这样做他马上会死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He'll die in seconds if we don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,多久？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.71,0:09:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你们…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How long...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,…睡了多久？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...have you been sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.00,0:09:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,两个世纪，我们估计\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Two centuries, we estimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,登陆小队呼叫总部，连接\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Landing party to Enterprise. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,登陆小队继续，已经连接\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go ahead, boarding party, we read you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,锁定麦考伊医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lock in on Dr. McCoy's beam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,一名遇难者随他一起传回\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's transporting back with a casualty we discovered here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.18,0:09:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真是壮观\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，补充\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, supplemental.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.53,0:09:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,在植物湾号旁已经停留十小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Alongside the SS Botany Bay for ten hours now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,包括工程师和医生的侦查小队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A boarding party of engineering and medical specialists
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.91,0:09:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,已经完成对神秘船只的侦查\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}are now completing their examination of the mysterious vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,待这个遇难者急救完毕后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Attempts to revive other sleepers
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:10:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将试图唤醒其他休眠者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}await our success or failure with the casualty already beamed over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊医生对他的强健体魄和恢复力深感惊奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. McCoy is frankly amazed at his physical and recuperative power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 登陆小组，这里是寇克 - 这里是史考特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Kirk to boarding party. - Scott here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特，有记录吗？日志什么之类的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Scotty, any records? Log books of any kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,没有，貌似在飞船起飞时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Negative, captain. It appears they were in suspended animation
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们是在假死状态 - 多少存活？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- when the ship took off. - How many alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,十二个睡眠舱已损坏，还剩七十二个在运作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Twelve units have malfunctioned, leaving 72 still operating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.15,0:10:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,其中三十人是女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thirty of those are women.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克下线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,存活了七十二人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Seventy-two alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,一群来自1990年代的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A group of people dating back to the 1 990s.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.33,0:10:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,重要的发现，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A discovery of some importance, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那一年代还有许多谜团\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are a great many unanswered questions about those years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你们历史上奇怪又暴力的年代\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A strange, violent period in your history.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有发现有关植物湾号的任何信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I find no record whatsoever of an SS Botany Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，DY-100号飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, the DY-100 class vessel
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,只能用作行星间旅行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}was designed for interplanetary travel only.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在那个时代，只有简单的核能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With simple nuclear-powered engines,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.94,0:10:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,想要星际航行根本不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}star travel was considered impractical at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他们能成功前往下一个星系的概率\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was 10,000-1
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是万分之一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}against their making it to another star system.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,而且，为什么没有旅行记录呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And why no record of the trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.40,0:11:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,植物湾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Botany Bay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是澳大利亚的海滨流放地，对吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...that was the name of a penal colony on the shores of Australia, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们以此命名…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If they took that name for their vessel--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想说这是艘流放船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you're suggesting this was a penal deportation vessel,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那你的结论完全违背逻辑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you've arrived at a totally illogical conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你的地球在暗黑年代的边缘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your Earth was on the verge of a Dark Ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,许多人都被炸死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whole populations were being bombed out of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,比起浪费飞船让罪犯们遨游太空\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A group of criminals could have been dealt with
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,还有更有效的处理方法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}far more efficiently than wasting one of their most advanced spaceships.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,对，我的推论就那么多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes. So much for my theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我还想听听你的理论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm still waiting to hear yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一个理论需要事实来支撑，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Even a theory requires some facts, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,目前为止…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So far...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还没有证据 - 这点让你恼怒了，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- ...I have none. - And that irritates you, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 恼怒？ - 对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Irritation? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有那种情绪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am not capable of that emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我的错，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My apologies, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.30,0:12:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你怀疑有危险？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You suspect some danger in them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不了解真相常常导致危险，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Insufficient facts always invites danger, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.18,0:12:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，那我最好套出些事实来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, I'd better get some facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 继续调查 - 是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Rig for towing. - Aye, aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 制定前往星际基地12的航线 - 是，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Make course for Starbase 12. - Aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That'll be all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 老骨头？ - 他没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Bones? - He'll live.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 干得不错 - 不，我医术没好到那种程度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- My compliments. - No, I'm good, but not that good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他体内有东西拒绝死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's something inside this man that refuses to accept death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,看这个，就算他病成这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, look at that. Even as he is now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:13:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他的心脏瓣膜也是你我的两倍强壮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}his heart valve action is twice the power of yours or mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,肺部效率是我们的1.5倍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lung efficiency, 50 percent better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,优良人种\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}An improved breed of human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是优生战争产生的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's what the Eugenics War was all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我估计他可以一手举起我俩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd estimate he could lift us both with one arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,要是他的智力赶上体力就有趣了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Be interesting to see if his brain matches his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，他会活下来吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doctor, will he live?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看来会的，上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It appears he will, lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.63,0:13:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我要和你谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd like to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,如果要我评价你今天登陆时表现…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I were to rate your performance as a member of the landing party today--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道，长官，对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know, sir. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉，请记住，每个船员的表现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant, at any one time, the safety of this entire vessel might depend
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,都会影响飞船的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}on the performance of a single crewman aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你找到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And the fact that you find a man
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,符合你个人喜好的男人…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}strangely compelling to you personally--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不是个人喜好，舰长，是专业方向\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not personally, captain, professionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我专攻历史\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My profession is historian,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,现在发现了来自过去的活标本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and to find a specimen from the past, alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我是指，研究他的想法将会很有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean, the sheer delight of examining his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:14:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,同时他们也富有冒险精神\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And men were more adventuresome then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,胆大，更多样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bolder, more colourful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没错，长官，的确如此 - 好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Yes, sir, I think they were. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我直言，此时更易忽略错误\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I can have honesty, it's easier to overlook mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.38,0:14:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 就这么多 - 好的，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- That's all. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你做指挥官真是可惜了，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A pity you wasted your life on command, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经成为公正的心理学家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'd have made a fair psychologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.48,0:14:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,公正？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,医务室呼叫实验室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sickbay to lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们有什么异常吗？ - 一切正常，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Anything new on those bios? - They all came out fine, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，麦考伊下线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good. McCoy out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,掐死我还是割破喉咙，选一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, either choke me or cut my throat. Make up your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.23,0:15:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这是英语，我似乎在梦里听过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}English. I thought I dreamed hearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我在哪儿？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where am l?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你在…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're in--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你在床上用刀抵着你医生的喉咙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're in bed holding a knife at your doctor's throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Answer my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.88,0:16:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,割断颈动脉会更有效\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It would be most effective if you would cut the carotid artery,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就在左耳下方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}just under the left ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢勇敢的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I like a brave man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是试图避免争吵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was simply trying to avoid an argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你在联邦星舰进取号上，你的船拖在后面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're aboard the United Spaceship Enterprise. Your vessel is in tow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得有个声音，是不是说…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I remember a voice. Did I hear it say...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我睡了两个世纪？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...I had been sleeping for two centuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的舰长在哪儿？我有许多问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where is your captain? I have many questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舰桥 - 我这儿有个病人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Bridge. - I have a patient here
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有很多问题要问，舰长 - 马上到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- with many questions, captain. - On my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,詹姆士·寇克，这艘星舰的指挥官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}James Kirk, commanding the starship Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.58,0:17:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你的名字是？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我先问几个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have a few questions first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你的飞船驶向哪里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What is your heading?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,驶向星际基地12，伽玛400星系中的行星…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our heading is Starbase 12, a planet in the Gamma 400 star system...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,它是这一区域的指挥基地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...our command base in this sector.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这样说可以吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that of any use to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我的属下…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,…怎么样了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...my people?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:18:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,七十二个生命维生舱仍在正常运行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Seventy-two of your life-support canisters are still functioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.37,0:18:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你会复苏他们 - 只有我们到了星际基地12\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You will revive them. - As soon as we reach Starbase 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那么…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字是可汗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Khan is my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 可汗，姓呢？ - 就是可汗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Khan. Nothing else? - Khan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.26,0:18:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你们起飞的具体日期是什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What was the exact date of your liftoff?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们知道是在1990年代初期，但…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We know it was some time in the early 1990s, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.68,0:18:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我有点累了，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I find myself growing fatigued, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,下次再谈这个问题好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}May we continue this questioning at some other time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要事实，可汗先生，只要一点时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The facts I need, Mr. Khan, will take very little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,比如，你们远征的性质\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For example, the nature of your expedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.78,0:18:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，等会再谈吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim, a little later might be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，在我恢复期间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, I wonder if I could have something to read
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:19:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,可以看一些书吗？我曾是工程师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}during my convalescence. I was once an engineer of sorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我对你们飞船的技术手册很感兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I would be most interested in studying the technical manuals on your vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好，我明白，你有两百年的知识要补\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, I understand. You have 200 years of catching up to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,的确\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,任何一个病人都可以从显示屏获悉这些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're available to any patient on the viewing screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊医生会告诉你如何使用图书馆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. McCoy will show you how to tie into the library tapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢，舰长，你很合作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you, captain. You are very cooperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.22,0:19:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这个可汗和我想象的20世纪人不同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This Khan is not what I expected of a 20th-century man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我注意到他在使用我们的技术库\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I note he's making considerable use of our technical library.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.60,0:19:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这是常见的礼节，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Common courtesy, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他将在我们的世纪度过余生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's going to spend the rest of his days in our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是帮他补上知识\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's only decent to help him catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.81,0:20:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他可不可能是…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.11,0:20:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,…优选种产物？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...estimate him to be a product of selected breeding?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有这个可能，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There is that possibility, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,按年龄来说有可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}His age would be correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.99,0:20:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在1993年，一群这样的超人类\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In 1993, a group of these young supermen
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,夺取了超过40个国家的主权\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}did seize power simultaneously in over 40 nations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.33,0:20:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他们简直是超人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, they were hardly supermen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他们激进傲慢，逐渐发生内战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They were aggressive, arrogant. They began to battle among themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,因为科学家们高估了一个事实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because the scientists overlooked one fact:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,超能力会孕育超级野心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Superior ability breeds superior ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.68,0:20:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,有趣，如果是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Interesting, if true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他们制造了一群亚历山大，拿破仑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They created a group of Alexanders, Napoleons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我收集了一些资料做了调查\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've collected some names and made some counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.57,0:20:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,据调查，当超人类们被击溃时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By my estimate, there were some 80 or 90
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,仍有八九十个下落不明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of these young supermen unaccounted for when they were finally defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,事实不是历史书上那样的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That fact isn't in the history texts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你难道会向那些厌战的人宣布\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Would you reveal to war-weary populations
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,仍有八十个拿破仑存活？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that some 80 Napoleons might still be alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.39,0:21:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 随船历史学家，上尉… - 玛拉·麦戈文\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Ship's historian. Lieutenant-- - Marla McGivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,据说你也参加了我的救援\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am told you participated in my rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.94,0:21:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,只帮了小忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In a small way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在了解船身结构\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've been reading up on starships, but they have one luxury
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但有件奢侈品手册里没提\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}not mentioned in the manuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.61,0:21:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.37,0:21:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,美丽的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A beautiful woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.83,0:21:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫可汗，请坐下陪我一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My name is Khan. Please sit and entertain me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.51,0:21:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我想了解你们飞船的历史\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd like some historical information about your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 飞船的目的是… - 你怎么把发型\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Its purpose and-- - And why do you wear your hair
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.64,0:21:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,弄得这么糟？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in such an uncomplimentary fashion?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.39,0:22:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这样很舒服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.35,0:22:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但并不漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But it's not attractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.12,0:22:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.38,0:22:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,自然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.80,0:22:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 简单 - 可汗先生，我是来办公事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Simple. - Mr. Khan, I'm here on business.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得这样很愉快吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You find no pleasure here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.02,0:22:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我专于科学，人…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My interest is scientific. Men of--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.06,0:22:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,以及过去的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is the world of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.81,0:22:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定明白，事实上，和你们世纪的人谈话…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sure you understand, actually to talk to a man of your century...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.52,0:22:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.28,0:22:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,简单\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.03,0:22:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,舒适\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.32,0:22:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,愉快的记忆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.08,0:23:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,也许改天你会更想谈过去的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perhaps some other time when you feel more like talking about the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.63,0:23:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴你能来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm glad you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.17,0:23:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你再来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.73,0:23:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真令人惊叹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.56,0:23:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们邀请了五星上将参加晚餐？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are we expecting a fleet admiral for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.36,0:23:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉麦戈文建议以此欢迎可汗来到我们世纪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant McGivers' idea to welcome Khan to our century.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.20,0:23:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,她到底对他多着迷？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just how strongly is she attracted to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.54,0:23:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，并没有条款禁止浪漫，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, there aren't any regulations against romance, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.08,0:23:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我是指公事上，不是个人感情上，老骨头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My curiosity is official, not personal, Bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.00,0:23:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，他有吸引力，几乎是电磁力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, he has a magnetism, almost electric. You felt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.55,0:24:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,对麦戈文来说这比历史还要吸引人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And it could overpower McGivers with her preoccupation with the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.05,0:24:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.31,0:24:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你能带我去参加晚餐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I hoped you might guide me to our dinner engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.57,0:24:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.94,0:24:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 画工很精细 - 这是名为弗拉维奥的角斗士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Fine technique. - It's a gladiator named Flavius.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.74,0:24:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他曾经… - 你为我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- He once-- - And you've rearranged
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.57,0:24:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,重新打理了头发\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}your hair for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.70,0:24:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.92,0:24:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,都是历史中有血性的男人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All bold men from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.21,0:24:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,查理德、莱夫·埃里克松、拿破仑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Richard, Leif Ericson, Napoleon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.47,0:24:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的男人，是你的兴趣？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A hobby of yours, such men?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.77,0:24:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我的荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am honoured.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.57,0:24:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.32,0:25:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我警告你…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I caution you...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.95,0:25:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,…这种男人敢拿他想要的任何东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...such men dare take what they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.10,0:25:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,原谅我的好奇心，可汗先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Forgive my curiosity, Mr. Khan,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.01,0:25:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但我的军官们想知道你的冒险经历\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but my officers are anxious to know more about your extraordinary journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.98,0:25:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你如何从历史书中钻出来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And how you managed to keep it out of the history books.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.81,0:25:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,冒险，舰长，是冒险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Adventure, captain. Adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.48,0:25:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,地球上什么都不剩了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There was little else left on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.07,0:25:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那场战争结束了暴政\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There was the war to end tyranny.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.15,0:25:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很多人认为这是高尚的行为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Many considered that a noble effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.57,0:25:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,暴政，先生，团结人类的手段？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tyranny, sir, or an attempt to unify humanity?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.66,0:25:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,统一，先生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unify, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.50,0:25:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就像鞭子下的动物吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like a team of animals under one whip?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.84,0:26:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这些年代的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know something of those years, remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.34,0:26:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,一个宏伟梦想的年代，一个伟大抱负的年代\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was a time of great dreams, of great aspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.01,0:26:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,在一系列独裁下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Under dozens of petty dictatorships.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.10,0:26:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,最终会有一人统治\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One man would have ruled eventually,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.81,0:26:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就像罗马在凯撒的统治下，想想他的成就\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as Rome under Caesar. Think of its accomplishments.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.03,0:26:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你的同情就…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then your sympathies were with--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.70,0:26:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你是一名卓越的战略家，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are an excellent tactician, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.20,0:26:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你让副指挥攻击…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You let your second-in-command attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.79,0:26:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,自己则坐观敌人弱点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...while you sit and watch for weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.87,0:26:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你似乎喜欢套用军事术语\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have a tendency to express ideas in military terms, Mr. Khan.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.43,0:26:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但这是社交场合\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is a social occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.51,0:26:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,据说社交场合暗藏战争\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It has been said that social occasions are only warfare concealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.98,0:27:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,很多人觉得社交更诚实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Many prefer it more honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.36,0:27:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,更开放\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}more open.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.23,0:27:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你逃跑了，为什么，害怕了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You fled. Why, were you afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.90,0:27:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我从未害怕 - 但你留在这个时代\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I've never been afraid. - But you left at the very time
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.28,0:27:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 需要勇气 - 我们掌管世界秩序\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- mankind needed courage. - We offered the world order!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.79,0:27:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.54,0:27:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,聪明，真聪明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Excellent. Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.43,0:27:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,请原谅，先生们和女士们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But if you will excuse me, gentlemen and ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.10,0:27:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我又一次疲乏了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I grow fatigued again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.98,0:27:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，请允许我回到我的住处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With your permission, captain, I will return to my quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.13,0:28:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wanted to apologise.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.63,0:28:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他们无权那样对你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They had no right to treat you that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.55,0:28:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,十分理解，因为对于这里来说，我是一团迷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Quite understandable, since I'm something of a mystery to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.27,0:28:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说你不是谜，我很清楚你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're no mystery to me. I know exactly who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.48,0:28:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.48,0:28:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,莱夫·埃里克森，狮心王理查德，拿破仑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Leif Ericson, Richard the Lion-Hearted, Napoleon.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.45,0:28:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不知你是否喜欢我们时代的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know if you're going to like living in our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.49,0:28:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那我不得不把它改造成我喜欢的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then I'll have to remold it to my liking.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.66,0:28:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拜托别 - 走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Please don't. - Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.83,0:28:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,要不然就自愿留下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or stay, but do it because it is what you wish to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.64,0:28:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如何？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.14,0:28:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我就再留一会儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll stay a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.02,0:29:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算客气多久？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How many minutes do you graciously offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.94,0:29:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我是说… - 我对此厌倦了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I only meant-- - This grows tiresome.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.73,0:29:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在得求我让你留下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You must now ask to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.19,0:29:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意留下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd like to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.53,0:29:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.39,0:29:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,打开你的心胸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Open your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.39,0:29:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你会对我坦诚吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Will you open your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.48,0:29:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.98,0:29:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要拿下这艘飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I intend to take this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.94,0:29:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你同意吗？ - 请别让我…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Do you agree? - Please don't ask me to--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.65,0:29:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.66,0:29:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会伤害其他人吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You won't harm anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.70,0:30:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在质问我？ - 没\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Now you question me? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.54,0:30:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你会帮我吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Will you assist me?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.21,0:30:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拜托，可汗，别让我… - 那滚吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Please, Khan, don't ask-- - Leave me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.84,0:30:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我说，滚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go, I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.76,0:30:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.06,0:30:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.77,0:30:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,一切顺从你的意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll do anything you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.88,0:30:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,姓名：可汗，正如我们今天所知\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Name: Khan, as we know him today.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.59,0:30:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,姓名：可汗·努尼恩·辛格\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Name: Khan Noonien Singh.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.06,0:30:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,从1992年至1996年，从亚洲到中东\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}From 1992 through 1996, absolute ruler
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.56,0:30:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是统治你们四分之一世界的独裁者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of more than a quarter of your world, from Asia through the Middle East.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.10,0:30:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,最后被推翻的暴君\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The last of the tyrants to be overthrown.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.69,0:31:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须承认，先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I must confess, gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.69,0:31:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直暗地里敬佩这个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've always held a sneaking admiration for this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.99,0:31:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他是最优秀的暴君，也是最危险的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He was the best of the tyrants, and the most dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.28,0:31:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,某种程度上，他们是超人类\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They were supermen, in a sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.91,0:31:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,强壮，勇敢，当然也野心勃勃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stronger, braver, certainly more ambitious, more daring.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.33,0:31:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们，对这个独裁者不能抱有浪漫主义思想…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gentlemen, this romanticism about a ruthless dictator is--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.46,0:31:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，野蛮是人类固有的特征\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock, we humans have a streak of barbarism in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.80,0:31:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管很可怕，但是事实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Appalling, but there, nevertheless.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.93,0:31:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他的统治下没有大屠杀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There were no massacres under his rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.68,0:31:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 也没有自由 - 为了反击他才发动战争\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- And as little freedom. - No wars until he was attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.85,0:31:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.94,0:31:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，你误解我们了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock, you misunderstand us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.02,0:31:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以同时敬仰他和反对他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can be against him and admire him, all at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.99,0:31:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不合逻辑 - 没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Illogical. - Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.36,0:31:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长呼叫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.24,0:31:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,对可汗房间实行24小时监控，马上执行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Put a 24-hour security on Mr. Khan's quarters, effective immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.55,0:32:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，舰长，我…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, captain, I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.26,0:32:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,…陷入沉思了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...lost in thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.10,0:32:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我的门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My door.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.85,0:32:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,从外面反锁了，还有人守着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Locked from outside, a guard posted.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.15,0:32:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,对可汗·努尼恩·辛格的特殊待遇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unusual treatment for Khan Noonien Singh.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.69,0:32:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,聪明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.41,0:32:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你是在电脑系统里找到的吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You identified me with your computer system, I imagine?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.99,0:32:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在就要你回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd like those answers now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.04,0:32:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,首先…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}First...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.08,0:32:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,…你们星际旅行的目的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...the purpose of your star flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.96,0:32:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,全新的生活，创造新世界的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A new life, a chance to build a world.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.51,0:32:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,其他事情我想你也不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Other things I doubt you would understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.89,0:32:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.18,0:32:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我不是控制遗传学的产物？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because I'm not a product of controlled genetics?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.81,0:33:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，虽然你的能力让我很感兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, although your abilities intrigue me...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.52,0:33:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你的精神和肉体上都更逊一筹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...you are quite honestly inferior. Mentally, physically.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.23,0:33:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上我很惊奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In fact, I am surprised how little improvement
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.03,0:33:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,多年来人类改善不大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}there has been in human evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.65,0:33:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，技术有所进步…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, there has been technical advancement...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.53,0:33:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,…但人类本身进步太小\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...but how little man himself has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.58,0:33:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,看来我们能在你们世纪做得更好，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, it appears we will do well in your century, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.59,0:33:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,还有其他问题吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you have any other questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.76,0:33:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.05,0:33:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我已得到答案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They've all been answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.64,0:34:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,让开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Move away.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.83,0:34:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,奥托\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.25,0:34:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,华金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Joaquin.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.75,0:34:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,旅途结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The trip is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.38,0:34:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,战争即将开始，只是这次，我们赢得的不是世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The battle begins again. Only this time, it's not a world we'll win,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.34,0:34:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,而是整个宇宙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it's a universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.51,0:35:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,卡蒂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kati.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.23,0:35:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 航线正确，舰长，2级曲速 - 继续维持\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- On course, sir. Warp factor 2. - Maintain.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.94,0:35:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舰桥 - 舰长，门卫倒下了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Bridge. - Captain, security here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.99,0:35:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可汗逃了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Khan's escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.86,0:35:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 打开安全警报 - 已开启，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Sound security alert. - Security alert, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.70,0:35:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,遭到通信干扰，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Communication channels are jammed, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.00,0:35:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,涡轮升降机不起作用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Turbo elevators inoperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.25,0:35:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,遭到干扰，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jammed, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.43,0:35:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,大气控制器被切断了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Atmospheric controls cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.56,0:35:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没用了，他们在轮机室获得了更高权限\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Useless. They're on override in Engineering.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.98,0:35:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,轮机室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Engineering.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.90,0:35:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,史考特，这里是舰桥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Scotty, this is the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.65,0:35:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.12,0:36:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 发生什么事了？ - 他此时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What's going on down there? - He's not able to answer you
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.24,0:36:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,无法回答你，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}at the moment, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.91,0:36:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你的船现在归我，我已经关闭了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your ship is mine. I have shut off the life-support system
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.92,0:36:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,舰桥的生命支持系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to your bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.92,0:36:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,关闭了你们的逃生通道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}jammed up your exit routes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.09,0:36:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎你们来洽谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am willing to negotiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.76,0:36:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,所有船舱覆盖类神经气体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Flood all decks with neural gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.93,0:36:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,无法实施，入侵者破坏了系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Impossible. Intruder control systems inoperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.56,0:36:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,可汗对我们的技术手册研究得很透彻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Khan was very thorough in his study of our tech manuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.44,0:36:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,联系星际基地12\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Contact Starbase 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.11,0:36:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,所有通道都被阻断，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All channels are totally jammed, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.95,0:36:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,聪明，每个应急措施都预料到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Brilliant. Every contingency anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.28,0:36:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,里面的空气现在肯定很稀薄了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your air should be getting quite thin by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.95,0:36:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们投降吗？ - 绝不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Do you surrender the bridge? - Negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.75,0:36:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,聪明点，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Academic, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.29,0:36:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,拒绝，舰桥上每个人都会窒息而死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Refuse, and every person on the bridge will suffocate.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.10,0:37:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,星历3142.8\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stardate 3142.8.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.31,0:37:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他们控制了我的船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They have my ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.81,0:37:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,抛弃了他们自己无用的飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...discarding their own worthless vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.69,0:37:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,舰桥现在仅剩少量空气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Only moments of air left on the bridge now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.62,0:37:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,应该嘉奖乌乎拉上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Commendations recommended for Lieutenant Uhura,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.21,0:37:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一级技术师哈里森和托雷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Technicians First Class Thule and Harrison...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.50,0:37:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,斯皮内利上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...Lieutenant Spinelli...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.01,0:37:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,当然还有史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...and of course, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.35,0:37:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我要负全部责任\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I take full responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.19,0:37:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我尽…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I take full...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.23,0:38:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,除了人以外…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nothing ever changes...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.20,0:38:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,其他事物一点没变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...except man.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.95,0:38:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你们获取了技术进步\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your technical accomplishments?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.16,0:38:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,改进机械装置，生产效率可以翻倍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Improve a mechanical device and you may double productivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.17,0:38:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但若改进人类…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But improve man...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.04,0:38:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你会获得一千倍，我就是这样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...and you gain a thousandfold. I am such a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.97,0:38:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Join me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.34,0:38:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会亏待你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll treat you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.22,0:38:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你操纵这艘复杂的船只\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need your training to operate a vessel this complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.22,0:38:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克舰长在哪儿？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where is Captain Kirk?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.19,0:38:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,看来我犯了个严重的错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I see now I made one serious error.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.23,0:38:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你是通信官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are the communications officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.57,0:38:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,启动屏幕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Engage the viewing screen, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.93,0:39:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.52,0:39:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该意识到，让你们在舰桥上一起窒息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I should have realised that suffocating together on the bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.78,0:39:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,可以创建你们之间的英雄情结\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}would create heroic camaraderie among you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.28,0:39:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但要坐着袖手旁观\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But it is quite a different thing to sit by
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.66,0:39:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,则困难许多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and watch it happening to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.04,0:39:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,请看屏幕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Engage the viewing screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.37,0:39:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该很清楚这个医疗减压室吧，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sure you recognise your medical decompression chamber here, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.72,0:39:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,也知道那气压计的意味\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And the meaning of that indicator.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.45,0:40:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的舰长将要死去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your captain will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.96,0:40:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你加入我们，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you join me, Mr. Spock...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.59,0:40:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我会留他一命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...I will save his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.93,0:40:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我的飞船没什么用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My vessel was useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.64,0:40:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你们的飞船来选择一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need you and yours to select a colony planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.18,0:40:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,会听从我们命令的殖民地星球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}one with a population willing to be led by us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.27,0:40:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,被你征服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To be conquered by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.85,0:40:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,有一艘星舰会使这更简单，不是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A starship would make that most simple, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.52,0:40:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你们每个人都会轮流进去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Each of you in turn will go in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.28,0:40:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人则看着他死去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Die while the others watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.12,0:40:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,可汗，我没有理由在这里看着吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Khan, there's no reason I must watch this, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.58,0:41:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你很坚强\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I hoped you would be stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.84,0:41:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,若有一人能加入我们，任何一人…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If any one of you joins me, anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.81,0:41:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,…我就会让他活着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...I'll let him live.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.06,0:41:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,反抗是无用的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's so useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.11,0:41:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的通讯受阻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've lost the channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.07,0:41:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们怎样才能获得画面？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How do I regain picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.53,0:41:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It does not matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.08,0:41:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长已经死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The captain is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.58,0:41:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克是下一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take Mr. Spock next.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.98,0:41:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,（减压室）
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.72,0:42:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,可汗说要密切关注他，他或许会同意合作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Khan said to watch him very closely. He may decide to cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.64,0:42:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我救了你，请别杀他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, I saved your life. Now, please don't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.49,0:42:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,看见你很吃惊，舰长，虽然也很欣慰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm surprised to see you, captain, though pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.95,0:42:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己也有点欣慰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm a little pleased myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.49,0:43:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 现在什么情况？ - 可汗在简报室挟持了我们的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Situation. - Khan is holding our staff
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.45,0:43:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他的属下控制了飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in the Briefing Room. His men have control of the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.67,0:43:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的唯一机会是入侵控制回路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our only chance is the intruder control circuit,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.67,0:43:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他把舰桥的回路切断了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}although he's cut it off at the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.42,0:43:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,沿着走廊走会有个中继器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's a relay junction down the corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.25,0:43:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,在其它所有甲板释放气体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gas all decks but this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.47,0:43:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,军械库，这里是可汗，报告情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Armoury, this is Khan. Report.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.52,0:43:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,罗德里格斯？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Rodriguez?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.85,0:43:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,凌？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ling?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.44,0:43:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,麦弗逊？有谁在吗？报告情况！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}McPherson? Anyone? Report status!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.63,0:43:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 可汗在哪？ - 不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Where's Khan? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.04,0:43:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,在气体进来时他冲了出去…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He got out just as the gas...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.72,0:43:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是寇克 - 除了轮机室，麻醉气体已释放完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Kirk here. - Anesthesia gas in all sections
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.18,0:43:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,有人刚刚隔断了那里的信号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}except Engineering. Someone just closed that line.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.52,0:44:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, acknowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.19,0:44:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,气体无法达到轮机室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unable to flood Engineering section.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.15,0:44:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我怀疑… - 这里是史考特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I suspect-- - This is Scott.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.73,0:44:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长正在前往轮机室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's headed for the Engineering section.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.82,0:44:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我紧跟其后，以防… - 不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I'll follow in case-- - Negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.73,0:44:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,趁麻醉持续，我们应该夺回船只\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We must retake the vessel while the anesthesia lasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.40,0:44:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在军械库碰面，这里已清理干净，史波克下线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Meet me in the armoury. I'm blowing it clear first. Spock out.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.39,0:44:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我的理解正确\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I understood your manuals...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.98,0:44:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那你的飞船正在过载…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...that's an overload in progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.77,0:44:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,几分钟后，它会像爆炸的太阳一样燃烧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your ship flares up like an exploding sun within minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.19,0:45:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我比你强壮五倍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have five times your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.11,0:45:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你打不赢我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're no match for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.72,0:46:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日记，星历3143.3\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 3143.3.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.52,0:46:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,飞船控制权已被夺回\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Control of the Enterprise has been regained.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.36,0:46:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望下一个决定不再如此困难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wish my next decisions were no more difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.03,0:46:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,把可汗和他的属下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Khan and his people,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.44,0:46:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,流放到教改中心真是浪费人才\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}what a waste to put them in a reorientation centre.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.07,0:46:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,麦戈文如何处置？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And what do I do about McGivers?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.58,0:46:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,卡带已准备好了，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Record tapes engaged and ready, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.71,0:46:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,听证会现在开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This hearing is now in session.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.34,0:46:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,根据星际舰队司令部赋予我的权力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Under the authority vested in me by Starfleet Command...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.85,0:46:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我声明所有指控和陈述\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...I declare all charges and specifications
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.60,0:46:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,已经处理完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in this matter have been dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.57,0:47:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，虽然同意你有权利…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jim, agreed you have the authority--
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.73,0:47:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，我认为我们正在驶向鲸鱼座阿尔法星系附近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock, I believe our heading takes us near the Ceti Alpha star system.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.45,0:47:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，舰长，五号行星可供居住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Quite correct, captain. Planet number five there is habitable,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.12,0:47:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有些荒芜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}although a bit savage, somewhat inhospitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.91,0:47:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但不比澳大利亚的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But no more than Australia's
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.08,0:47:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,植物湾流放地差\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Botany Bay colony was at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.08,0:47:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那些人是去征服一片大陆的，可汗先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Those men went on to tame a continent, Mr. Khan.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.71,0:47:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你能征服整个世界吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you tame a world?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.42,0:47:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你看过弥尔顿吗，舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have you ever read Milton, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.76,0:47:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,看过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.10,0:47:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.39,0:47:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,玛拉·麦戈文上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant Marla McGivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.78,0:47:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在军事法庭审判和跟他们一起流放当中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Given a choice of court-martial
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.61,0:47:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,二选一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or accompanying them there...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.12,0:47:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,流放很艰辛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It will be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.33,0:47:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,历经千辛万苦，需要为生存而战、需要觅食\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A struggle at first, even to stay alive, to find food.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.13,0:48:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我和他一起，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll go with him, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.01,0:48:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,坚强的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A superior woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.76,0:48:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我会带上她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I will take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.14,0:48:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我得到了其他我想要的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I've gotten something else I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.39,0:48:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,需要征服的世界，在建的帝国\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A world to win, an empire to build.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.32,0:48:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,听证会结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This hearing is closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.00,0:48:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然身为苏格兰人，但我却没读过弥尔顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a shame for a good Scotsman to admit it, but I'm not up on Milton.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.76,0:48:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,当堕天使路西法掉入深渊时曾说过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The statement Lucifer made when he fell into the pit:
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.88,0:48:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,“与其在天堂做奴隶，倒不如在地狱称王”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"It is better to rule in hell than serve in heaven."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.27,0:48:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一百年后再来看这个世界一定会很有趣，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It would be interesting, captain, to return to that world in 100 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.19,0:49:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,去看看你今天种的种子开出何种花果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...and learn what crop had sprung from the seed you planted today.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.07,0:49:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.78,0:49:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,的确如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It would indeed.
